extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p.lead This lab uses the MVC pattern. Database queries are in Model classes, not in the routes.

  .row.mt-4
    .col-md-4
      .card.mb-3
        .card-body
          h5.card-title Model
          p.card-text Classes that handle all database queries (StudentModel, ProgrammeModel).
    .col-md-4
      .card.mb-3
        .card-body
          h5.card-title View
          p.card-text Pug templates that render the HTML shown to the user.
    .col-md-4
      .card.mb-3
        .card-body
          h5.card-title Controller
          p.card-text Express routes that connect the model and the view.

  .alert.alert-info.mt-2
    strong Key difference from Lab 7:
    |  Routes no longer contain SQL. They call model.get(), model.insert(), model.remove() instead.
